channel.title: Need to get rid of .java's
channel.description: I let my friend play my server and he told me he could still see (and use) the .java files, but i looked at a different 317 server, and it was all .class files, how can I make it so its all .class files?

now if you want to get rid of java files just delete them off of your client before releasing it since the jvm only needs class files.

item.title: Need to get rid of .java's
item.dc:creator: @Mr_Bobby Mr. Bobby
item.description:
@Mr_Bobby wrote:

he probly has his folder options set to “see hidden files” and you dont, open up a folder and hit the alt key
then go to tools>folder options>view tab> find where it sais show hidden files and folders and check it and wala u can see files hidden by people. now if you want to get rid of java files just delete them off of your client before releasing it since the jvm only needs class files.
